(21, 1, '2013-03-07 16:30:09', '2013-03-07 16:30:09', '<h3>2013</h3>\r\n<h4><a href="?page_id=26">Hanging Bruce-Howard</a></h4>\r\nLloyd Bruce-Howard is a hung-over, washed up, actor looking his next big break. Over a raucous afternoon in his crumbling apartment he must face, a stalker, an angry ex-wife, a dramatic Russian billionaire amongst others, all demanding his hazy attention. <a href="?page_id=26">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n<h3>2012</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="?page_id=71">Ruthlessness</a></h4>\r\nThe year is 1997, and it all rests on a rigged boxing match, a vote on super-casino permits, and two hapless lowlifes. Meet the new boss: same as the old boss? <a href="?page_id=71">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="?page_id=66">Good Grief</a></h4>\r\nThree siblings are brought together following the death of their estranged father. The show takes place at the hectic funeral, and later at the even more farcically chaotic wake, and depicts the siblings’ struggle to deal with their own personal dramas on top coming to terms with their father’s death. Years of suppressed tensions between the six characters come to the surface under the influence of large quantities of wine and a batch of hash cookies. <a href="?page_id=66">Read more...</a>', 'Shows', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'shows', '', '', '2013-03-16 02:35:56', '2013-03-16 02:35:56', '', 0, 'http://perform.susu.org/gonerogue/?page_id=21', 0, 'page', '', 0),
