ng in the festive spirit, here&#8217;s what our Media Departments have been getting up to:</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.soundcloud.com/surgemusicteam/surge-aid-surge-another-day"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-5826" style="border: 0px" src="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/Surge-Christmas-player.jpg" alt="" width="311" height="209" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Surge Radio, have had some live sessions from local artists <a title="Hear Triassic''s Christmas cover here" href="http://surgeradio.co.uk/features/129/Christmas_Session_Triassic" target="_blank">Triassic</a> and <a title="Hear Dan''s Christmas cover..." href="http://surgeradio.co.uk/features/130/Christmas_Session_Daniel_Tovey" target="_blank">Daniel Tovey</a>, but have also got together their DJs to take part in recording their <a title="Hear the Surge DJs destroying this Christmas classic..." href="www.soundcloud.com/surgemusicteam/surge-aid-surge-another-day" target="_blank">annual Christmas song</a>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.susu.tv/series/advent-calendar-2012/"><img class="alignright  wp-image-5830" style="border: 0px" src="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/susutv-player-540x302.jpg" alt="" width="378" height="211" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>SUSUtv have been creating videos every single day of December all based around this special time of year. You can look back through their <a title="Ho Ho Ho!" href="http://www.susu.tv/series/advent-calendar-2012/" target="_blank">Advent Calendar</a> and see the festive treats.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.wessexscene.co.uk/series/art-advent/"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-5832" style="border: 0px" src="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/ws-art-image-540x360.jpg" alt="" width="324" height="216" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Wessex Scene have been getting artistic in their Winchester section. You can check out their <a title="it''s beaauuuutiful..." href="http://www.wessexscene.co.uk/series/art-advent/" target="_blank">Art Advent</a> and see some beauty across this winter month.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.theedgesusu.co.uk/features/2012/11/17/10-alternative-christmas-songs-to-freshen-your-seasonal-playlist/"><img class="alignright  wp-image-5834" style="border: 0px" src="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/edge-songs-540x404.jpg" alt="" width="324" height="242" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The Edge have been counting down their <a title="and there''s still some more to go... " href="http://www.theedgesusu.co.uk/film/dvd-bluray/" target="_blank">100 disks of Christmas</a> &#8211; the top 100 films to shove in a stocking this year + giving you the low down on some <a href="http://www.theedgesusu.co.uk/features/2012/11/17/10-alternative-christmas-songs-to-freshen-your-seasonal-playlist/" target="_blank">alternative xmas songs to play around the house</a>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Hope that you all have a fantastic break from Uni and a great Christmas&#8230; don&#8217;t wear anything too embarrassing&#8230;</p>\n<p style="text-align: center"><a href="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/santa-and-elf.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5838" style="border: 0px" src="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/santa-and-elf-540x405.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="405" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"xmlns";a:6:{s:7:"content";s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";s:3:"wfw";s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";s:2:"dc";s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";s:4:"atom";s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";s:2:"sy";s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";}}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:69:"http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/2012/12/14/merry-christmas-everyone/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"