 involved in creating news content here at the University of Southampton.</p>\n<p>With external speakers coming down to inspire and inform a generation of students in creating news, this is a great opportunity to take advantage of. You don&#8217;t have to be involved with SUSU Media to take part &#8211; any student can come &#8211; but we do have limited spaces.</p>\n<p>If you want to take part then just <a title="There are only 50 spaces available" href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/viewform?formkey=dGZSWmlpN291TUR0YTZhektTTUN5X0E6MQ#gid=0" target="_blank">fill in this form to book a place</a>. We are expecting to run a further session in the new year, so if you can&#8217;t make this date, don&#8217;t worry &#8211; there are plenty of chances throughout the year to get involved in SUSU Media.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Please note that already half the places have been booked, so put your name down on the form quickly if you&#8217;d like to get involved and start your journalist journey before Christmas.</p></blockquote>\n<div id="attachment_5653" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 483px"><a href="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/anchorman41.jpg" target="_blank"><img class="size-full wp-image-5653 " style="border: 0px" src="http://blogs.susu.org/sabbs/files/2012/12/anchorman41.jpg" alt="" width="473" height="473" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">You stay classy, Southampton&#8230;</p></div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"xmlns";a:6:{s:7:"content";s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";s:3:"wfw";s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";s:2:"dc";s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";s:4:"atom";s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";s:2:"sy";s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";s:5:"slash";s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";}}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:69:"http://blogs.susu.org/